/dannyimusic/status/872102493605462016|website=Twitter|publisher=(Self-published)|accessdate=2017-06-11|date=2017-06-06|language=en|archive-date=2022-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220405182614/https://twitter.com/dannyimusic/status/872102493605462016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Ingram|first1=Daniel|title=[Scoring Finishing]|url=https://twitter.com/dannyimusic/status/874049208373972992|website=Twitter|publisher=(Self-published)|accessdate=2017-06-11|date=2017-06-11|language=en|archive-date=2022-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220405182002/https://twitter.com/dannyimusic/status/874049208373972992}}</ref>。

