==宣傳及發行==
2015年8月7日，[[獅門娛樂|獅門娛樂]]確認它們將於全球範圍（除中國外）發佈和推廣本電影<ref name=dl>{{cite web|last1=Lieberman|first1=David|title=Lionsgate Plans 'My Little Pony' With Kristin Chenoweth, VR For 'John Wick'|url=http://deadline.com/2015/08/lionsgate-my-little-pony-kristin-chenoweth-jon-feltheimer-1201494998/|publisher=Deadline|accessdate=2015-08-10|date=2015-08-07|language=en|archive-date=2022-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220604145629/https://deadline.com/2015/08/lionsgate-my-little-pony-kristin-chenoweth-jon-feltheimer-1201494998/}}</ref><ref name="mlp03">{{cite web|url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/the-magic-of-friendship-comes-to-the-big-screen-in-a-new-my-little-pony-movie-from-hasbros-allspark-pictures-and-lionsgate-300125402.html|title=The magic of friendship comes to the big screen in a new My Little Pony movie from Hasbro's Allspark Pictures and Lionsgate|publisher=PR Newswire|date=2015-08-07|accessdate=2016-07-13|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150810024156/http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/the-magic-of-friendship-comes-to-the-big-screen-in-a-new-my-little-pony-movie-from-hasbros-allspark-pictures-and-lionsgate-300125402.html|archive-date=2015-08-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref><!--Joe Ballarini-->。本電影在[[第69屆坎城影展|第69屆坎城影展]]和其它8部獅門娛樂負責的電影一起展示於眾，希望可以將電影銷售給國際分銷商<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/cannes-lionsgate-now-you-see-me-3-my-little-pony-1201769595/|title=Cannes: Lionsgate Selling ‘Now You See Me 3,’ ‘My Little Pony’|first=Dave|last=McNary|publisher=Variety|date=2016-05-10|accessdate=2016-07-13|language=en|archive-date=2022-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220528094609/https://variety.com/2016/film/news/cannes-lionsgate-now-you-see-me-3-my-little-pony-1201769595/}}</ref>。

《彩虹小馬大電影》原本預計2017年11月3日上映<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2015/film/news/my-little-pony-movie-release-date-1201642503/|title=‘My Little Pony’ Movie Gets Release Date|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|date=2015-11-18|accessdate=2015-11-19|last=McNary|first=Dave|language=en|archive-date=2015-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151119142837/https://variety.com/2015/film/news/my-little-pony-movie-release-date-1201642503/}}</ref>，隨後提前至2017年10月6日<ref name="release" />。正片放映前將放映同為孩之寶工作室製作的網絡劇集《[[Hanazuki:_Full_of_Treasures|Hanazuki: Full of Treasures]]》的動畫短片<ref>{{cite web|last1=Corvoda|first1=Chevistian|title=[Toy Fair 2017 confirmation of Hanazuki short]|url=https://twitter.com/Chevistian1/status/832606596861566977|website=Twitter|publisher=(Self-published)|accessdate=2017-02-18|date=2017-02-17|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210527203606/https://twitter.com/chevistian1/status/832606596861566977}}</ref>。電影的私人首映式則已在2017年9月24日於[[紐約市|紐約市]]的AMC Loews Lincoln Square 13劇院舉行<ref name="private"/>。

