孩之寶製作了不少基於電影角色、佈置和道具的玩具，並已於2017年8月1日發佈大批產品<ref>{{cite web|url=http://files.shareholder.com/downloads/HAS/3568268195x0x938743/3A2228A9-EDCC-4326-A400-C9061BEDA5D8/Hasbro_Q1_2017_Earnings_Management_Remarks.pdf|title=Hasbro First Quarter 2017|page=5|access-date=2017-05-11|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170806141441/http://files.shareholder.com/downloads/HAS/3568268195x0x938743/3A2228A9-EDCC-4326-A400-C9061BEDA5D8/Hasbro_Q1_2017_Earnings_Management_Remarks.pdf|archive-date=2017-08-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2016 PonyRadioCon討論會中簡短地預覽了一些計劃的商品（包括T恤和圖樣等）<ref name="PRC Geek"/>。2016年7月27日，[[彩虹小馬可蒐集卡片遊戲|彩虹小馬可蒐集卡片遊戲]]在Twitter上暗示了新一套基於電影的卡片<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/MLP_CCG/status/758363605121335296|title=MLP: CCG hinting on future card set|publisher=Twitter|author=MLP: CCG|date=2016-07-27|accessdate=2016-09-12|language=en|archive-date=2022-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220413172510/https://twitter.com/MLP_CCG/status/758363605121335296}}</ref>。孩之寶為電影設計的玩具線於[[美國國際玩具展覽會|美國國際玩具展覽會2017]]和其它不少玩具展中被展示及推廣<ref>{{cite web|url=http://comicbook.com/2017/02/17/new-york-toy-fair-my-little-pony-movie-toys/#|title=My Little Pony the Movie Toys Unveiled at Toy Fair|work=ComicBook|first=Russ|last=Burlingame|date=2017|accessdate=2017-05-11|language=en|archive-date=2020-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200329050508/https://comicbook.com/2017/02/17/new-york-toy-fair-my-little-pony-movie-toys/}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iWQk3LcA3sI|title=NEW 2017 My Little Pony Toys! MLP Movie, Sea Ponies, Magical Princess Twilight Sparkle!|work=YouTube|publisher=Bins Toy Bin|date=2017-02-20|accessdate=2017-05-11|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200829151456/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iWQk3LcA3sI&gl=US&hl=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/HasbroNews/status/857585129035845633|title=[Pony at TTPM]|work=Twitter|publisher=Hasbro|date=2017-04-27|accessdate=2017-05-11|language=en}}</ref>。{{link-en|Entertainment Earth|Entertainment Earth}}則為電影推出了毛絨玩具，開始分階段於它們網站上發佈<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.entertainmentearth.com/prodinfo.asp?number=HSB9820A|title=[EE Wave 1 Plushies listings]|work=[[Entertainment_Earth|Entertainment Earth]]|accessdate=2017-05-11|language=en|archive-date=2017-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170901045832/http://www.entertainmentearth.com/prodinfo.asp?number=HSB9820A}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.entertainmentearth.com/prodinfo.asp?number=HSB9820B|title=[EE Wave 2 Sea pony Plushies listings]|work=Entertainment Earth|accessdate=2017-05-11|language=en|archive-date=2017-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170806141543/http://www.entertainmentearth.com/prodinfo.asp?number=HSB9820B}}</ref>。

